10 weeks post-ACL reconstruction and Kanav’s feeling stronger than ever! 
Grateful to get an opportunity to work with someone so diligent who put his trust in me 100 percent☀️
Staying back in Mumbai for 3 months only to get better faster before heading back to Chicago 🥇

💪🏽 This journey has been challenging, but every bit of progress — from early rehab to now — reminds us of the power of patience, dedication, and perseverance. Kanav has been committed to only improving, focusing on building strength, improving stability, and regaining confidence in his knee. While there are still milestones to reach, I’m proud of how far Kanav has come and motivated himself to keep pushing forward. This recovery process has taught us resilience and the importance of listening to one’s own body. Grateful for the support of everyone at the @thetribeindia and the progress I see in Kanav every day! Here’s to continued strength, healing, and getting back to full activity — stronger and smarter than before! 🙌🔥 #ACLRecovery #RehabJourney #StrongerEveryDay #KeepPushing #patientandpersistent
